BRIEF-Eagle Energy Announces Final Approval Of The Transfer Of Listing From The TSX To The TSX Venture Exchange

Stock Markets 1 hour ago (Oct 07, 2019 17:50)

© Reuters. BRIEF-Eagle Energy Announces Final Approval Of The Transfer Of Listing From The TSX To The TSX Venture Exchange Oct 7 (Reuters) - Eagle Energy Inc : * EAGLE ENERGY INC. ANNOUNCES FINAL APPROVAL OF THE TRANSFER OF LISTING FROM THE TSX TO THE TSX VENTURE EXCHANGE * EAGLE ENERGY INC - TRADING SYMBOL WILL CONTINUE TO BE "EGL" ON TSX-V
